Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alice.\N-Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I fail yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rewrite it as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we received the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Communication is cut off in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After the people of New Himuka\Nwatch this footage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be mass protests outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
