Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere to embrace me♫
