Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You'll see I'm always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller\Ncoaster inside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and the unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
