Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
