Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,ARAHABAKI'S TRAP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain eater will exert immense strain\Non the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Karen's motive anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he travel through time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he teleported away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He copied the power but couldn't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If Karen needs to travel through time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He might need both Kasane's and Yuito's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I must stop Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, you must be worried about Yuito too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for protecting me until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Meddling vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, are you going to copy Yuito's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ambush failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way you can win now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you should know by now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if I will it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make you perish in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're after Yuito's brain power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't risk damaging his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can break his limbs with no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if I paralyze him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will copy his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We inherited the legacy from Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have our revenge on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-The Moon?\N-What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they are just commoners,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,linking thousands of them together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,will give us enough power for the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By linking more brain power users,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka's military might
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"THE MOON? THIS MUST BE A JOKE!"\Nwill reach a whole new level!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"WHAT HAPPENED?"\NHe can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even users like us can't handle\Nthe load from SAS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need is their brains and body parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the troops to Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have received waves of inquiry calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, we need you at the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he was strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't expect to master\Nmultiple powers at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more troublesome than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true he can use multiple powers at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is only one brain\Nthat's processing the powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the winner has the right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you can never defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These red threads... They are from Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the invasion was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, what is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?\NWhat is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"DANGER"\NI remember the time Kasane and I resonated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The invasion has reached the depth of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Arahabaki controlling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Karen's true motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to start all over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,protected Kasane and got rid\Nof Togetsu's troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are always trying your best\Nto catch up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I must do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu sent troops after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen tied us all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But only Yuito lost his consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We were forcefully invaded by Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Yuito's brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His brain has been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Major General Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared after taking Yuito's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,forget all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain talk isn't working either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Yuito's memories are slowly being deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-You mean...\N-Yuito won't remember his entire life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst cases,\Nhis mind will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hate to see that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories make us who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Without them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the Yuito, as we know, will be gone for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no way to help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could copy our memories to Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that even possible?\N-Yes, it might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can link our memories together\Nand fill in the gaps in his.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill in the gaps? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can turn our memories into data\Nand transfer them to Yuito
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,via SAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be using our memories\Nto overwrite his.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are certain risks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is our only option now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We must stop Yuito's mind from destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\None of the rehabilitation researches
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was about the theory of memory transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, tell me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll provide program support.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we doing it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-But there might be some issues...\N-Then fix them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we can save Yuito,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bit of hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, I like that kind of personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi, keep calling out for Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,External stimuli could slow down\Nthe memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the program is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Check everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to maintain the symbolization of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Regeneration, confirmation, and reconstruction\Nmust be maintained in the form of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But the key is Yuito's brain structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We must target the correct memory section\Nfor it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just the thing to get that done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the scan data of Yuito's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it would come in handy someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have this, Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, all of you touched the terminal\Nin Togetsu for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They secretly scanned it back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I deleted the data right after I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely made a backup copy\Njust in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we can set the memories\Nto their correct sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Coordinate locked on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same location where\Nthe brain anomaly took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all that's left is executing the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can connect to SAS now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider that anesthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about memories related to Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito...\N-The voices are beckoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I must go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A curfew has been issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Citizens of New Himuka, do not be deceived\Nby false information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please abide by the information released\Nby the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay inside your houses or indoor and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-If there is any emergency...\N-What false information?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't allow us to go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-They were talking about invading the Moon!\N-Is the media our government's lapdog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who stand against the government\Ndo not belong in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, it's nearly impossible\Nto keep the information under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the most capable censoring system
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot stop the people\Nfrom speaking their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my brother's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't expect it to turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We must change New Himuka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so we won't regret this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we finally regrouped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's so somewhere safe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and discuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads\Ninto the ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,KAREN'S AMBITION
